text: Diana Lynn Olson (born February 27, 1969) is an American rower. She competed in the women's eight event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:American female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of the United States Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Anchorage, Alaska
